---
title: Cantonese-Style Noodles with Beyond Meat®
description: This tasty veggie knock-off has it all! The Beyond Meat® gets punched up with ginger and garlic before getting tossed with tender bok choy, filling cabbage and carrots, chewy chow mein noodles and a salty soy and teriyaki sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nouilles-a-la-cantonaise-04906d9a.jpg
